( To make use of literals easier, we keep two "scratch" bytes allocated on
  the D stack, at 0,x and 1,x. Below this is top, and below that, second.
  Like this:

     |      |      |
     +------+------+
  4  |  sh  |  sl  |  5   second
     +------+------+
  2  |  th  |  tl  |  3   top
     +------+------+
  0  |  xh  |  xl  |  1   scratch
     +------+------+
)

